Hello, could you help me please
Hi there! I'm here to help. What can I assist you with today?
I need help with adjust tracking
Sure, I can help with that! Could you please let me know which tracking platform or service you're using for Adjust tracking? This will help me provide more specific guidance.

Great! For setting up tracking with Adjust, you can follow these steps:

1. Search and select "NewsBreak" in the "Network" section of Adjust.
2. Name your tracker and click "Customize."
3. Copy your tracking URLs to NewsBreak's Ad Manager.

For more detailed instructions, you can refer to this article: [Introduction to App Install Events](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/26530008151309-Introduction-to-App-Install-Events). Let me know if you need further assistance!
